values:
Geuss whos back...back again...Billdo's back...tell some women!

Not a whole lot of shit going on since the last time I talked to ya. School is going good, lots of studying but I will be alright. I survived another hurrican....GAY. Im gonna end up quiting my job at Papa Joes becuase the 250 can't handle it and im supposed to be getting a more feul efficiant car but who knows. Mabey I will put in apps at home depot or lowes....AGAIN. Im tired of girls! And I havent been surfing at all not even to the beach...WTF?

Well I got more studing to do and im just not feeling this journal tonight so I will say Late!

Wow....Been a while since I have updated this thing so im gonna summarize the last few weeks for ya. 

We got hit by a fucking hurricane! Me being the dumbass I sometimes am decided to go driving down 419 while the wind was blowing 70 plus mph in my truck. Let me tell ya my 250 is a bad bitch, it didnt even get pushed off the road a lil, I was proud of her. Chulouta got fucked up bad...well preety much oviedo geneva and all of central FL did. 

I got a new job, where do you ask? This lil Itialian restraunt called Papa Joes. Its a preety badass job and I make decent money.

I bought a surfboard! Well acually I still owe Buck some money but it was a great deal. Its a Matt Kechele board with some minor damage but hey its a good first board and since I'll be going to Peru with my rents in the fall and I always wanted to learm to surf, then why not now. 

I ride at station 42 in Geneva tomarrow.....SO EXCITED. I get to ride 24 hrs too so it should be fun. Mabey some dumbass redneck will light a field on fire and ill get to go out in the woods truck.

School starts next wednesday and I can actually say im excited to start even though i know itll get old fast atleast ill be one step closer to finacial stability.

Well im Outty, and remember never eat yellow snow! LATE!

I got accepted into the EMT program at Seminole....YES! Im excited and can't wait to start. I gotta go to Al's Army Navy and get a bunch of new BDU's and boots and the best thing is mommys paying because its for school. I just one step closer to conquering one of my most important goals. Friday I gotta go get a mass amount of fucking shots for school, oh well atleast I can get it outta the way.

Today I finnaly got a liscense plate for my badass truck so I don't have to sweat balls bout driving it illigally anymore. Gotta go to court tomarrow for doin that shit. Oh well im good at kissin ass, lol. Well fuck I dont got much shit to say so I'll say PEACE and have a good night.

So yeah I had my regular Seminole County Explorers meeting tonight. Preety much the same as always except for our new PT before class, what a joke! Anyway so Cj and I along with Shay John Justin Matt his gf or whatever and Alan are all in driving down 1792 headed to P.F Changs when bam this car runs a red and rearends another car. It was awsome I got to get out and stand there and act like I knew what I was doin lol while the real EMT's did there thing. Evryone was ok, happy ending. I even got to wear gloves lol. Changs was awsome.....Orange peel chicken, brown rice......AMAZING as shay would say lol. Well anyway not much else going on and im gonna go to bed becuase I have to work 8 hrs tomarrow. Good night all

GOD DAMNIT! I just wrote a bunch of shit and then I hit rich text mode and alllllllll of it got deleted. MOTHER FUCKER!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

I'll start over, Today is gay I have been working on my house the whole day. From cutting the grass and weed whippin to power washin this humungo concrete wall that surrounds my house.......that is until I broke the nozzel so now I have to go buy another powerwashing gun, DAMNIT!....just had to get that out.

On a better note, MACHINE HEAD at the house of blue later this month, YESSSSSSSS! Not to mention the PROJECT REVOLUTION TOUR.....Linkin Park, Korn, Less Than Jake, The Used and Snoop. I have to make some money real soon.

Well I have to go now cause well I have to so Peace out and kaylee or however the hell you spell it is a BITCH.

So ya last night was fun. got off work and headed out to old schools house and got stalked by some girls on the way...got be the truck, lol. Ended up being Me, Old School, CJ Shay, Bud light, Bud, and Coors. Have you ever had one of those nights where your so preoccupied by something that you just cant catch a buzz no matter how much or fast you drink? Well that was last night for me so I basically sat around board playin xbox and watching drunk ppl have fun, Oh well. I can't wait for school to start as bad as that might sound. I just wanna get thru EMT and get to Standards where the real fun will be. Hell Ill be glad when my career acually starts and im making more money than I know what to do with....wait I know....F250 powerstroke superduty and a new street bike, perhaps a 636 or mabey I'll get stupid and get a Liter bike. But for now I have to go moves brick pavers around for 8 hours. As Cj would say, "Late"!
Ok my bad its entry....Hey do you know any smart firfighters??????? I did'nt think so.

I dunno if i spelled entrie right but oh well. This my first entrie and my first time using live journal. I have benn reading a few ppls journals and i figured this would be a good way for me to get stuff out bla bla bla. Im a little pissed cause its not letting me upload any pictures but oh well i will figure it out. Today sux becuase i have to work around the house in order to make enough money to put insurance on my new old f 2 fiddy so i dont go to jail on wednesday when i go to court....... well i have to go back to work it was fun cya later.
